      "value": "<p>If you move at least 10 feet in a straight line toward a target immediately before hitting it with a melee attack roll as part of the Attack action, choose one of the following effects:</p><p><strong>Extra Damage.</strong> <span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\">Double the damage modifiers dealt by this attack.</span></p><p><strong>Shove.</strong> If it is no more than one size larger than you, push the target up to 10 feet away or cause it to have the &amp;Reference[Prone] condition.</p><p>You can use this benefit only once on each of your turns.</p>",
